PhysicalTable.name: SAMP_TARGETS_F
PhysicalTable.Description: Targets fact table. Stores the target facts information at Month, Office and Product grain.

PhysicalColumn.name: Revenue
PhysicalColumn.Description: Revenue: Stores the target revenue information as a double.

PhysicalColumn.name: Prod_Key
PhysicalColumn.Description: Product Key: Joins to Prod_Key of Products dimension table.

PhysicalColumn.name: Office_Key
PhysicalColumn.Description: Office Key: Joins to te Office_Key of Offices dimension table.

PhysicalColumn.name: Units
PhysicalColumn.Description: Units: Stores the target units information as an integer.

PhysicalColumn.name: Bill_Mth_Key
PhysicalColumn.Description: Bill Month Key: Joins the Mth_Key of Time dimension table (Mth grain).

PhysicalColumn.name: Bill_Qtr_Key
PhysicalColumn.Description: Bill Quarter Key: Joins to Qtr_Key of Time dimension table (Qtr grain).
